In spirit of celebration, Dbanj, the Kokomaster has congratulated a fan who won N1million for his 42nd birthday bash. He had announced on Thursday that he would give out N1m to a fan to make his birthday. Bangalee expressed gratitude to God for making his ‘face to show, keeping his shoe shining and his teeth white promised to gift N1million to a lucky fan who BIDs the lowest unique number on Cream Dela Cream Bid.   Nigeria records 10 new monkeypox cases in seven days     D’Banj celebrates 42nd birthday in grand style     Politics in Nigeria not for faint hearted – Davido   “Grateful to God for another year so I must celebrate it specially. Grateful to God for making my face to show, keeping my shoe shining and my teeth white as I add another year today. “In the spirit of celebration, I will be giving out 1M naira to a lucky fan who BIDs the lowest unique number on Cream Dela Cream Bid, a product under the Cream Platform”, he wrote. Announcing the winner hours later, Dbanj congratulated the fan identified as Joseph Victor. The singer wrote: “Congratulations to the winner Of Dbanj one million naira Birthday cash. Joseph Victor. Winner =0803225***7. Winining Bid =122. Thanks @creamplatform and @parallexbankng. “Victor: your face show, your shoe shine: your teeth white.”